{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://thomasgriffin.io/using-wordpress-as-a-saas-platform-with-optinmonster/#disqus_thread\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 26 Jul 2015 17:00:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://thomasgriffin.io/?p=1525\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2230:\"<p>I&#8217;m super excited to be presenting here at WordCamp Asheville about using WordPress as a SaaS (software-as-a-service) platform with OptinMonster.</p>\n<p>If you haven&#8217;t heard yet, <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com\" target=\"_blank\">OptinMonster</a> is by far the most popular product I&#8217;ve built to date. It has accumulated a huge following, and as of recently, <a href=\"http://optinmonster.com/announcing-optinmonster-app-the-biggest-update-to-optinmonster-since-the-launch-of-optinmonster-itself/\" target=\"_blank\">we moved OptinMonster to a hosted platform built on WordPress</a>.</p>\n<p>Here are slides for the talk. You can find the links I used within the slides below the embedded presentation. Enjoy!</p>\n</p>\n<p>Slide Links</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.slideshare.net/griffinjt/using-wordpress-as-a-saas-platform-with-optinmonster\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.slideshare.net/griffinjt/using-wordpress-as-a-saas-platform-with-optinmonster</a><br />\n<a href=\"https: